* &quot;Courtship Habits of the Great Crested Grebe&quot; (1914) &quot;A landmark in ethology.&quot;
* &quot;Essays of a Biologist&quot; (1923)
* &quot;Essays in Popular Science&quot; (1926)
* &quot;The Stream of Life&quot; (1926)
